    en: "When a loved one dies, the grief is overwhelming and the logistics are immediate. Death certificates, funeral arrangements, benefits notifications, and legal matters all need attention — sometimes within days. This guide walks through the practical steps and where to get help in Monroe County, including when families cannot afford a funeral."
